    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1870550/extras/0a67b9b187389b8c841b2a7db15cc864.poster.avif?t=1763761389\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1870550/extras/0a67b9b187389b8c841b2a7db15cc864.webm?t=1763761389\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1870550/extras/0a67b9b187389b8c841b2a7db15cc864.mp4?t=1763761389\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>《海盗巢穴》是一款真正、全面的模拟经营游戏，背景设定于海盗的黄金时代，玩家作为一名退休海盗，试着料理一个荒芜的热带小岛。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1870550/extras/e034c4f6ca2357f851b226d79d2be83a.poster.avif?t=1763761389\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1870550/extras/e034c4f6ca2357f851b226d79d2be83a.webm?t=1763761389\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1870550/extras/e034c4f6ca2357f851b226d79d2be83a.mp4?t=1763761389\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>明智地管理预算，在第一批客人到达前做好一切准备，或是见机行事，选择具有挑战性的方式，时机和快速决策对于避免破产至关重要。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1870550/extras/ed2af36cc0391faea5fdf9fc39371b09.poster.avif?t=1763761389\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1870550/extras/ed2af36cc0391faea5fdf9fc39371b09.webm?t=1763761389\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1870550/extras/ed2af36cc0391faea5fdf9fc39371b09.mp4?t=1763761389\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>承担一份工作，例如酒保、木匠、造船工、帆船油漆工、值班经理、酒馆老板、商人，或是干脆雇人帮您做这些事！设置优先事项和外包任务是老板的主要职责，在海盗世界也是如此！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1870550/extras/8b69df26aed33629c19b8f9e9a089a4a.poster.avif?t=1763761389\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1870550/extras/8b69df26aed33629c19b8f9e9a089a4a.webm?t=1763761389\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1870550/extras/8b69df26aed33629c19b8f9e9a089a4a.mp4?t=1763761389\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>根据游戏故事线，海盗想在岛上平静度过第二次青春，但仍需履行先前职业的义务。当您日子过得不错时，总会有人记得很久以前您向人借的这堆金子。 <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1870550/extras/a4ac6d4a1eb861b0f76c2bad090aa4ae.poster.avif?t=1763761389\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1870550/extras/a4ac6d4a1eb861b0f76c2bad090aa4ae.webm?t=1763761389\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1870550/extras/a4ac6d4a1eb861b0f76c2bad090aa4ae.mp4?t=1763761389\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>主要特色：<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>在荒芜的热带小岛上重建、翻新和经营一个真正的海盗湾。<br></li><li>用各式各样的酒馆、商店和造船厂，吸引船员和独来独往的海盗。<br></li><li>雇佣并管理员工，将生意做起来。<br></li><li>根据您的喜好定制海港、建筑和内部装饰。 <br></li><li>事无巨细地管理各种统计数据，从街道清洁到员工薪酬，以及对海盗的尊重。</li></ul>",
